* Changed the token ttl to 60 seconds to be safe

* Some refactoring

* Removed unnecessary comments from tests

commit.message:
Add testing for current Django versions (#200)

* Test multiple Django versions

* Remove/change deprecated Django modules

* Make all tox envs run on Travis

* Scope sqlite3 patch and apply for Django

Previously the patch was global which caused the django tests to fail if
the sqlite3 tests weren't also run.

* Fix tox environments for Django
